{"tid":1760129,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【優品360中期少賺6% 將到內地開舖】","createTime":"2019-11-28T04:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T04:19:15.000Z","uid":240511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4dc4ed139011bf939a92754c99f331b69c4022c5","tid":1760129,"uid":240511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:10:45.000Z","msg":"喂，福建幫間野先跌得6%，裝修不力喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//捲入反修例風波的優品360(2360)，中期純利按年下跌6%至1,345萬；收入按年升14.7%；中期息每股1.5仙。<br />\n<br />\n公司話，自今年6月社會運動爆發以來，對店舖業務運作造成負面影響，加上訪港旅客人數減少，致純利倒退。公司仲透露，截至星期三(11月27日)，一共有75間舖頭，喺社會運動中遭受唔同程度破壞，正同保險公司商討及處理相關賠償安排，若保險公司拒絕賠償或賠償額不足，將面對相關經濟損失。<br />\n<br />\n公司預計，本港零售市道短期內仍充滿挑戰同不確定性，形容社會運動「持續並具破壞性」，香港業務正被動地及顯著地受到影響。所以公司已開始研究於內地開設零售業務嘅可行性，預期下個財政年度首家設於內地嘅分店將會開業，期望成為新嘅增長勢頭。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XTWtqt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XTWtqt&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtOUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=f61f0eca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XTWtqt</a><br />\n <br />\n#優品360<br />\n#中期業績<br />\n#香港零售<br />\n#零售市道<br />\n#aastocks//"},{"pid":"609b1b5b3ebf94ea87773a6006865a7c84515ba1","tid":1760129,"uid":303133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:11:16.000Z","msg":"先6%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fb225fb0e1772030b3645728871c2041766c28","tid":1760129,"uid":75582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:11:32.000Z","msg":"唔蝕仲有賺Wor"},{"pid":"0740e29b67be9274c57968c85969627dac92453b","tid":1760129,"uid":133514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:12:01.000Z","msg":"唔洗食零食丫？ <br />\n你開間比我"},{"pid":"22123f5ecf4433c4947bff61b755c4d2c4dfd2b5","tid":1760129,"uid":330472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:19:15.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁都賺錢"}]}